{"tid":1364880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然咁多遍地開花post 不如搞個工會","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T02:02:52.000Z","uid":48655,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d976617601d4ff326f126afc555034f790fbeb72","tid":1364880,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"有部分比較多人嘅行業 例如<br />\n銀行 保險 零售 工程 運輸 等等<br />\n我見遍地開花簽名嘅人隨時有過千人<br />\n<br />\n不如每個行業都各自開一個tg<br />\n如果夠多人 日後行動要再升級 聯署/罷工/工業行動都會容易同有組織得多<br />\n呢兩日睇雖然覺得好正 但都洗走左好多其他post<br />\n雖然而家無集體談判權 但起碼多個平台發聲<br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a41d100f1d0acdacc6addd89b7b0ce67f81112b","tid":1364880,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"268a53d64eb3179ae4f4199d440415e0102bc263","tid":1364880,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bf250c50bc116c96968241418e1b49b2eb78ee61","tid":1364880,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"遍地開花"},{"pid":"3ef3ded45327bd2b835687f1842831d4df793523","tid":1364880,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:17:25.000Z","msg":"遍地開花"},{"pid":"924367f1493082f126a02f6d24f7c68fa19f3ca6","tid":1364880,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"[香港李鵬]點解元朗恐襲之後仍然冇人識鄧炳強<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16eef624bd227e2b12d80b054b98dbfefe7164a0","tid":1364880,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s